{"tid":102952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人跟車真係煩撚過閪","createTime":"2017-02-01T03:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T04:14:01.000Z","uid":40324,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b09359969e1fe7a0a32109122c299263f6bf6fa2","tid":102952,"uid":40324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"拎左p牌兩個月倒 前後借屋企人車揸過三次<br />\n次次揸都係你隔離開喇叭咁無停過口<br />\n想專心少少揸都唔得<br />\n講埋晒啲無謂野 又重覆幾十次<br />\n前幾日新年嬲到停低架車叫佢自己揸返<br />\n自己未有車一定要借車先有得揸<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"3ca7605ec6d9c64accc3e36ae7e728693fca43a0","tid":102952,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"講咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話你揸得衰係好合理,牌齡兩個月就想追到揸開車嘅人嘅技術根本唔可能<br />\n講其他廢話就抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e18bd3e799783c497341c802da204a24827ac2a","tid":102952,"uid":40324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話你揸得衰係好合理,牌齡兩個月就想追到揸開車嘅人嘅技術根本唔可能<br />\n講其他廢話就抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似聲控你揸架車咁<br />\n前面有單車打燈擰頭望車cut線慢車停車...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條路70揸緊60都話你太快<br />\n拖慢架車埋路口又話你做咩停低架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d94916f4579e1bb3cbb536bdf7f09ea30a88aa","tid":102952,"uid":66201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"自己買部車就唔洗煩<br />\n<br />\n當年一pass就去睇車，拎P當日下午去車房自己渣走部車<br />\n<br />\n間唔時會車下屋企人，但佢地唔敢出聲話我渣成點，始終車主係我，佢地唔滿意可以坐車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cfc67b6923bc4e87fb6ed69df87deae0f4bc92","tid":102952,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話你揸得衰係好合理,牌齡兩個月就想追到揸開車嘅人嘅技術根本唔可能<br />\n講其他廢話就抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似聲控你揸架車咁<br />\n前面有單車打燈擰頭望車cut線慢車停車...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條路70揸緊60都話你太快<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拖慢架車埋路口又話你做咩停低架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n過多幾個月你諗返就未必會講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為其實啱啱考到牌頭幾個月<br />\n個揸法對揸開車嘅人嚟講,係極恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,紅字就睇情況<br />\n如果你後面有車,你呢個係阻街行為<br />\n你可以諗下,你後面架車明明睇住你前面空晒<br />\n無諗過你咁早減速之下,你減緊速喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發緊夢果d真係會撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢d學車係唔會理,因為後車應該留2秒距離<br />\n但係香港人揸車,個個都係得1秒左右<br />\n所以實際揸車係要考慮埋後車嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}